        "action": "Amend planning regulations to help enable commercial on-site living spaces",
        "additional_details": "I think implementing on-site housing could help reduce daily commuting time, lower transportation expenses and allow employees to focus more on their work. I think it could foster a more supportive work environment, potentially boosting morale and creativity. Some studies suggest that such environments can increase productivity and job satisfaction.",
        "background": "Amend planning regulations to help facilitate the provision of on-site accommodation in commercial properties, making it easier for companies to offer on-site living spaces in offices.",
